metadata.name: close the door
metadata.description:
"On the basis of controlling the airflow, the cycle of life and death is the key, and Yin and Yang are the bottleneck, stopping thousands of ascetics, alas!" The white - faced scholar shook his head slightly, his face a little unnatural.



Control the airflow? Life and death? Yin and Yang? Is this what the practitioner should experience? That sounds scary. What is airflow? How can the cycle of life and death be achieved? Are the two poles the sun and the moon? What is the bottleneck? Zi Yang said in his mind.



The boy often came to shuju to eavesdrop. He knew the meaning of some words, but he could only guess and analyze the majority of figures by relying on the pronunciation of the words.
